::Feline::

She looked at Zardus again and stepped away from him.  She 
transformed into bot mode and stood next to Zardus.  She put her 
hands on his shoulder and rushed the tip of her tail against the back 
of his neck.  She kept one hand on his shoulder and the other roamed 
around his back.  She purred softly. She looked at Skulletron."Is 
this the one you want me to work with? Very well, I shall do my best 
what ever the assignment." She slowly saundered over to Skulletron 
and put her hand on his shoulder.  She looked him up and down. "Not 
bad. At least you gave me someone with an impressive appearance 
Zardus." She smiled at Skulletron. She walked back over to 
Zardus, "So, what's the plan?"
